message: "If you use Latency Hunter Toolkit, please cite it as below."
title: "Latency Hunter Toolkit"
abstract: >-
  Quant-engineering skills for Claude Code — a plugin bundling five skills:
  backtest-guard (backtest pitfall audit), latency-audit (C++ low-latency
  hot-path review), connector-forge (Binance/OKX connector scaffolding),
  orderbook-sanity (market-data quality audit) and risk-config-lint
  (risk-management config audit). No alpha, no keys, no models — engineering only.
type: software
